 "intro_html": "Whilst it might seem like an amenable grade and reasonable length, this is a serious adventure on rock that is loose in places with limited reliable protection in places. Expect a long day our for this adventure! The route takes the landward facing ridge to the summit. You will need a small boat or canoe to get to the base and ideally a very calm sea in order to make a reasonably safe crossing. Expect a complicated descent requiring some down climbing and abseiling.",
